Here's the simplified proposal formatted in LaTeX, with the budget adjusted to 4,000,000 IQD:

```latex
\documentclass[a4paper,12pt]{article}
\usepackage[margin=1in]{geometry}
\usepackage{setspace}
\usepackage{hyperref}

\hypersetup{
    colorlinks=true,
    linkcolor=blue,
    filecolor=magenta,      
    urlcolor=cyan,
}

\title{Proposal for Climate Consultant Expert Services}
\author{[Your Name]}
\date{\today}

\begin{document}

\maketitle

\section*{1. Project Understanding}
Five One Labs seeks to integrate climate resilience practices into its 32-session Incubator Program curriculum. This initiative aims to equip entrepreneurs in the Kurdistan Region of Iraq (KRI) with the tools to address local environmental challenges while aligning with global sustainability goals.

\section*{2. Technical Approach \& Methodology}

\subsection*{Key Steps}
\begin{enumerate}
    \item \textbf{Curriculum Review}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Analyze all 32 sessions to identify opportunities for integrating climate resilience concepts.
        \item Draft a session-by-session outline with proposed climate-related enhancements.
    \end{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Content Development}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Create or adapt slides, trainer notes, and case studies in English, focusing on climate resilience and sustainability.
        \item Translate all materials into Arabic and Kurdish to ensure accessibility.
    \end{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Finalization \& Handover}
    \begin{itemize}
        \item Refine materials based on feedback from Five One Labs.
        \item Provide a Trainer Guide with talking points and references.
        \item Conduct a final handover session to ensure smooth adoption of the curriculum.
    \end{itemize}
\end{enumerate}

\section*{3. Work Plan \& Timeline}

\textbf{Duration}: January 21 – February 25, 2025 (5 weeks)

\begin{center}
    \begin{tabular}{|l|l|l|}
        \hline
        \textbf{Step} & \textbf{Deliverables} & \textbf{Timeframe} \\
        \hline
        1. Curriculum Review & Climate Integration Outline & Week 1–2 \\
        \hline
        2. Content Development & Climate-Integrated Curriculum (English, Arabic, Kurdish) & Week 3–4 \\
        \hline
        3. Finalization \& Handover & Complete Curriculum Package + Handover Session & Week 5 \\
        \hline
    \end{tabular}
\end{center}

\section*{4. Financial Bid}

\textbf{Total Lump Sum: 4,000,000 IQD} (Inclusive of all project expenses, translation, and taxes)

\begin{center}
    \begin{tabular}{|l|l|}
        \hline
        \textbf{Step} & \textbf{Rate (IQD)} \\
        \hline
        Curriculum Review & 1,200,000 \\
        \hline
        Content Development & 2,000,000 \\
        \hline
        Finalization \& Handover & 800,000 \\
        \hline
        \textbf{Total} & \textbf{4,000,000} \\
        \hline
    \end{tabular}
\end{center}

\section*{5. Payment Terms}
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{Schedule}: One-time payment upon completion of all deliverables (by February 25, 2025).
    \item \textbf{Method}: Bank transfer or bank letter.
    \item \textbf{Currency}: IQD (inclusive of taxes).
\end{itemize}

\section*{6. Closing Statement}
Thank you for considering this proposal. My objective is to provide a practical, impactful climate-focused curriculum that empowers entrepreneurs to create sustainable businesses in KRI. Please feel free to contact me for any questions or clarifications.

\textbf{Sincerely,} \\
[Your Name] \\
[Your Title/Position] \\
[Your Email Address | Phone Number]

\end{document}
```

You can copy and paste this code into any LaTeX editor (e.g., Overleaf) to generate the final document. Adjust placeholders like `[Your Name]` and `[Your Email Address]` to personalize it.
